267
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:14,130
Beef?

268
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:22,260
The thing is… Actually…

269
00:22:32,440 --> 00:22:34,310
Oh my. What's with her?

270
00:22:57,670 --> 00:23:00,800
I'm not going to run away
without paying the bill, okay?

271
00:23:01,220 --> 00:23:04,550
You know where I live
and my social security number too.

272
00:23:05,550 --> 00:23:09,430
Neulpureun Hospital is so big.
How can you be so heartless?

273
00:23:10,890 --> 00:23:12,850
I won't run away
without paying the hospital bills.

274
00:23:13,940 --> 00:23:15,350
Yes, I will!

275
00:23:15,690 --> 00:23:18,570
I'll make sure to pay my child's bills
even if I have to sell my organs,

276
