300
00:24:44,110 --> 00:24:45,030
A round of applause!

301
00:24:51,330 --> 00:24:53,790
-All right!
-Mr. Noh!

302
00:25:17,600 --> 00:25:18,850
We're here.

303
00:25:40,250 --> 00:25:42,040
It was 31,700,000 won.

304
00:25:42,840 --> 00:25:46,840
