just working for me without pay.

329
00:28:16,070 --> 00:28:17,610
Darn it.

330
00:28:19,990 --> 00:28:22,410
What about your hubby
Mr. Noh Manners' memories?

331
00:28:24,500 --> 00:28:26,620
No, it's not that.

332
00:28:29,170 --> 00:28:31,040
Then what? What's wrong?

333
00:28:41,680 --> 00:28:43,100
Nothing. Forget it.

334
00:28:44,430 --> 00:28:47,100
CEO PARK YANGTAE

335
00:28:58,450 --> 00:29:01,070
It's… finally today.

336
00:29:01,580 --> 00:29:02,830
Yes, sir.

337
00:29:05,910 --> 00:29:08,580
How much time
do we have left counting down?

338
00:29:10,670 --> 00:29:12,630
Exactly 30 minutes, sir.

339
00:29:12,960 --> 00:29:15,210
They'll be released in 30 minutes.

340
00:29:27,430 --> 00:29:28,940
Noh Gojin!

341
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:33,070
I'll make sure you pay for humiliating me!

