00:31:25,510 --> 00:31:27,140
MA EUNJUNG

370
00:31:29,510 --> 00:31:30,350
Yes, sir.

371
00:31:33,940 --> 00:31:37,150
Ms. Ma? Yes. How is Mr. Noh Manners doing?

372
00:31:40,940 --> 00:31:42,860
Mr. Noh didn't come to work today,

373
00:31:43,280 --> 00:31:46,070
and Mr. Oh only came
to the research office briefly and left.

374
00:31:46,570 --> 00:31:48,870
Why didn't Mr. Noh
come to the office today?

375
00:31:51,410 --> 00:31:52,790
Knowing his personality,

376
00:31:53,410 --> 00:31:57,130
maybe he fainted…
from his rising blood pressure.

377
00:31:57,960 --> 00:31:59,170
That's it!

378
00:31:59,250 --> 00:32:02,260
Knowing Mr. Noh Manners' personality,
I'm sure he fainted.

379
00:32:03,010 --> 00:32:05,430
At this rate,
maybe he won't make it to KPEDA either.

380
00:32:06,220 --> 00:32:07,430
Perhaps.

381
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:12,220
Congratulations on your success, sir.

382
00:32:12,310 --> 00:32:15,310
I owe my success to you, Ms. Ma.

383
00:32:15,810 --> 00:32:17,310
Just hang in there a little longer.

384
00:32:17,650 --> 00:32:22,570
Ilpum Edu will
pave your way for teaching soon.

385
00:32:22,650 --> 00:32:23,570
Thank--

386
00:32:27,570 --> 00:32:29,280
Thank you, sir.

387
00:32:31,120 --> 00:32:32,200
Salute!

388
00:32:39,080 --> 00:32:42,050
What's going on? Why did you tell me
not to come to the office?

389
00:32:43,050 --> 00:32:46,050
Actually, there's a problem at work.

390
00:32:46,630 --> 00:32:48,840
