before you got into the accident.

393
00:32:54,930 --> 00:32:59,900
Ilpum Edu released study guides
that are almost identical to ours today.

394
00:33:01,060 --> 00:33:03,650
On top of that,
it was an explosive success

395
00:33:03,730 --> 00:33:05,530
with the first set of copies
sold out in a day.

396
00:33:07,360 --> 00:33:11,740
If they're almost identical,
they're the same, right?

397
00:33:12,830 --> 00:33:13,790
Yes, that's the case.

398
00:33:15,330 --> 00:33:16,830
How is that possible?

399
00:33:16,910 --> 00:33:20,790
I know. I feel ashamed as the deputy CEO.

400
00:33:20,880 --> 00:33:21,750
Perhaps,

401
00:33:23,040 --> 00:33:25,710
someone from our side
leaked the materials?

402
00:33:25,800 --> 00:33:27,590
I thought about that too,

403
00:33:27,670 --> 00:33:30,930
but rather than reprimanding
the teaching assistants in research,

404
00:33:31,010 --> 00:33:35,680
we should urge them to release
different study guides quickly.

405
00:33:35,970 --> 00:33:37,060
What do you think?

406
00:33:39,230 --> 00:33:41,980
Okay. I'll go with your suggestion.

407
00:33:43,270 --> 00:33:46,610
I take your word for it
when it comes to most things.

408
00:33:49,070 --> 00:33:53,950
So I take your word for it
when it comes to most things, however…

409
00:33:54,830 --> 00:33:55,870
What's wrong?

410
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:58,210
What? Nothing.

411
00:33:58,370 --> 00:34:00,290
Thank you, Gojin. I'll take care of it.

412
00:34:01,540 --> 00:34:04,540
Oh, right. And this.

413
00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:08,800
What is it?

414
00:34:09,170 --> 00:34:10,720
The Korean Private Education
Development Association.

415
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:12,340
It's a group for industry personnel.

416
00:34:12,930 --> 00:34:15,260
