for their tenth anniversary.

417
00:34:15,350 --> 00:34:17,520
We have to RSVP our attendance by today.

418
00:34:17,600 --> 00:34:19,850
Since it'll be hard for you to go,
I'll go on your behalf.

419
00:34:19,940 --> 00:34:22,310
No. I'll go.

420
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:24,730
But you won't remember
any of the members--

421
00:34:24,810 --> 00:34:28,030
I just need the members' information
ahead of time. I can memorize it quickly.

422
00:34:29,070 --> 00:34:29,900
Somehow,

423
00:34:31,030 --> 00:34:33,740
I have a feeling
that it's going to be very interesting.

424
00:34:37,370 --> 00:34:38,910
If you're so worried,

425
00:34:41,210 --> 00:34:42,580
I'll go with Ms. Sina.

426
00:34:44,540 --> 00:34:45,880
Me?

427
00:34:46,880 --> 00:34:48,670
No, I'm not going.

428
00:34:48,760 --> 00:34:51,300
Please go with him.
I won't be so worried then.

