454
00:37:08,140 --> 00:37:09,810
She used a man who has amnesia,

455
00:37:09,900 --> 00:37:13,440
pretended to be his fiancée, and committed
a billion-won fraud. That's a gold digger.

456
00:37:13,530 --> 00:37:15,860
But she had a good reason--

457
00:37:16,190 --> 00:37:18,490
All crooks have their reasons.

458
00:37:18,570 --> 00:37:20,620
There is nothing more to talk about.

459
00:37:20,990 --> 00:37:23,830
Don't bother getting a lawyer.
Go tell her to turn herself in right away.

460
00:37:23,910 --> 00:37:26,870
-Turn herself in?
-If she wants leniency.

461
00:37:28,620 --> 00:37:32,960
Is there… no other way?

462
00:37:34,130 --> 00:37:35,460
There is just one.

463
00:37:36,340 --> 00:37:37,300
What is it?

464
00:37:39,470 --> 00:37:42,390
Do everything the victim says
no matter what

465
00:37:42,890 --> 00:37:43,850
and negotiate well.

466
00:37:45,310 --> 00:37:48,810
That's the only way out, Ms. Lee Sina.

467
00:38:01,490 --> 00:38:02,990
How did he know my name?

468
00:38:03,070 --> 00:38:03,990
