469
00:38:06,450 --> 00:38:07,450
Whatever.

470
00:38:08,080 --> 00:38:13,040
God, please let me get out of this mess.

471
00:38:20,180 --> 00:38:21,470
Darn it!

472
00:38:23,550 --> 00:38:25,010
When your phone rings,

473
00:38:25,600 --> 00:38:29,770
