not yet available in the store.

502
00:42:02,940 --> 00:42:05,780
You're so beautiful
no matter what you wear, Ms. Baek.

503
00:42:05,860 --> 00:42:08,360
Everyone's going to be stunned
when they see you.

504
00:42:11,030 --> 00:42:12,030
No.

505
00:42:12,700 --> 00:42:16,740
There's only one person I want to stun.

506
00:42:21,330 --> 00:42:25,960
I want to be the most beautiful woman
in his eyes today.

507
00:42:34,050 --> 00:42:35,180
That one.

